# Instance data — the WW2 story "Nijmegen in de oorlog, 1940–1945".
# Eight narrative segments. NOTE: this file uses ONLY the existing ontology classes
# (Event/Place/Source/Photograph/AudioRecording/Quote/Story/Segment/*Block/MapState/
# Arrow). Adding a segment = append an Event + a MapState + a Segment + its Blocks.
# All media are real, sourced, openly-licensed (see Notes/verhalen/sources-ww2-*).
@prefix nmg:    <https://nijmegenkaart.nl/ns#> .
@prefix id:     <https://nijmegenkaart.nl/id/> .
@prefix schema: <http://schema.org/> .
@prefix dct:    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix owl:    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs:   <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix xsd:    <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix wd:     <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> .

